Using Todo Lists

* Adding / Viewing / Deleting Todo Lists

  Select the "Todo Lists" tab in the upper menu.

[images/todo_lists.png]

* Sharing Todo Lists

  Todo Lists can be shared amongst users: just click on the "edit" link, and add or remove users.

[images/share_todo_list.png]
